{"tid":1995481,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"邊度買switch比較抵？(33)報料請加密 比啲掙扎","createTime":"2020-04-30T09:37:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T11:27:55.000Z","uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"04c9155bb7bb1114590ad4305b9a041ed9c2f0e0","tid":1995481,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T09:37:27.000Z","msg":"動物森友會隻game正常價係399-430hkd<br />\n覺得實體版太貴可以買eshop版都係430hkd，唔洗食炒<br />\n<br />\nring fit就700蚊以下先係正價，呢隻就冇得買eshop版<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zGsgDn7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzGsgDn7.png&h=764635dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n細機lite就1490<br />\nlite機係玩唔到ring fit同某d遊戲，請留意返<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">港版特別主機(電力加強版)</span></strong> <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>※並非數量限定商品。日後將預定再次生產</strong></span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">-(<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.com.hk/topics/article/a_200131_02.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Ftopics%2Farticle%2Fa_200131_02.html&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=b95ca3c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.com.hk/topics/article/a_200131_02.html</a>)</span><br />\n己發售<br />\n預訂店鋪一覽: (官方頭盔: ※預訂及商品在庫狀況因店舖實際情況而異，詳情請向各店店員查詢)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.com.hk/hardware/switch/store/animal.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fhardware%2Fswitch%2Fstore%2Fanimal.html&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=78a50add\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.com.hk/hardware/switch/store/animal.html</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">入手請幫襯UNY/APITA/AEON/豐澤</span></strong> (唔經狗源藍絲代理拎貨)<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/animal_crossing_new_horizons/set/img/img-main-06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fswitch%2Fanimal_crossing_new_horizons%2Fset%2Fimg%2Fimg-main-06.jpg&h=56e37b2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n避深藍代理&amp;藍店攻略<br />\n<br />\n主機方面建議去豐澤/Aeon/Uny, 佢地係唔經代理商直接同任天堂拎貨<br />\n遊戲建議去eShop買下載版遊戲 或 幫襯黃店買水貨<br />\n<br />\n支那版中国貨switch千祈唔好買，因冇得online既殘缺閹割版<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gamewikia.com/uploads/2019/12/19/1.1-a7802cf61a78b0c1b6e3d5f849cbb280.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgamewikia.com%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F19%2F1.1-a7802cf61a78b0c1b6e3d5f849cbb280.jpg&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=9eaee843\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gamewikia.com/uploads/2019/12/19/1.1-a7802cf61a78b0c1b6e3d5f849cbb280.jpg</a><br />\n千祈唔好買<br />\n<br />\n食唔食炒，肯食幾多炒就自己衡量，唔係限量版，不斷會有貨返<br />\n希望各位入手到正價機同祝身體健康<br />\n<br />\n有關黃藍黑店請追 <br />\n<br />\n黃藍黑Game舖大集合 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686000/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686000/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZsGE0OV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZsGE0OV.png&h=c354e2f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img1.kakaku.k-img.com/Images/prdnews/2020013/20200131105806_970_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.kakaku.k-img.com%2FImages%2Fprdnews%2F2020013%2F20200131105806_970_.jpg&h=a95b9208&s={SIZE}\" />很想要吧？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n機主討論post，買完機可以入去討論交流<br />\n<br />\n|Switch機主討論(137)|<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1985955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1985955</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSwitch / 3DS 二手買賣區 (34)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1973433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1973433</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n|Switch|健身環大冒險 RingFit Advanture (16) 炒狗死全家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1993826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1993826</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[Switch]集合啦！動物森友會｜動物之森 討論區 (xx）<br />\nhttps://個度爆post速度太快廢事搵link自己打上面個名搜尋"},{"p